title: MoonMasters - The Johnny Red Eyes
description:
Predominantly recorded in 2013 at Euphonic Sound Studio, MoonMasters is the first full-length LP released by The Johnny Red Eyes.
credits
released 27 July 2014

All Music by: The Johnny Red Eyes
All Lyrics by: The Johnny Red Eyes
Produced by: Brian Steels and Eric Berall
Artwork by: Robert Parkinson

Recorded at Euphonic Sound Studio, Toronto, Canada.
Additional recording done at Brian, Rob and Eric's houses. 

I have been given expressed permission to upload this torrent from the band.

If you like them, check them out and like them on facebook to get updates.

More music to come, Enjoy and Seed!!!
